### ============================
### Session API — V1 CRUD
### ============================

### List all sessions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions
Accept: application/json

### Get a single session (replace {{session_id}} with a real ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions/{{session_id}}
Accept: application/json

### Create a new session (requires ORGANIZER JWT)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_organizer}}

{
  "title": "Cloud-Native Java in 2026",
  "abstract": "A look at the state of cloud-native Java development.",
  "level": "INTERMEDIATE",
  "track": "Cloud",
  "speakerId": "spk-duke",
  "roomId": "room-hall-a",
  "startTime": "2026-10-16T11:00:00",
  "durationMinutes": 50
}

### Update a session (requires ORGANIZER JWT)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions/{{session_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_organizer}}

{
  "title": "Cloud-Native Java in 2026 — Updated",
  "abstract": "Updated abstract with new content.",
  "level": "ADVANCED",
  "track": "Cloud",
  "speakerId": "spk-duke",
  "roomId": "room-hall-b",
  "startTime": "2026-10-16T11:00:00",
  "durationMinutes": 90
}

### Delete a session (requires ORGANIZER JWT)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions/{{session_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_organizer}}

